      <title>辉瑞将减持 Haleon 股份，发行 5.4 亿股</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/pfizer-to-pare-back-haleon-stake-with-540-million-share-offering</link>
      <description><![CDATA[辉瑞公司计划出售价值 5.4 亿股 Haleon Plc 股票，以削减其对这家英国消费健康巨头的持股。]]></description>
